column1: #Text=is a small city in Emerald Coast region of Florida , forty miles east of Pensacola .
#Text=Serves Fort Walton Beach and nearby Valparaiso .
#Text=American Eagle , Delta Air Lines , Delta Connection , United Express serve the airport .
#Text=US 98 connects Fort Walton Beach with Pensacola and Panama City .
#Text=Fort Walton Beach has two main arterials .
#Text=The Miracle Strip Parkway ( US 98 ) travels along the seacoast and through Eglin Air Force Base , and the Eglin Parkway ( Florida SR 85 ) links the city with Okaloosa Regional Airport .
